{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4bbe06d518","title":"关于陇东问题谈判的条件给谢觉战的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"11aa1a8de5","index":0,"year":1940,"month":1,"day":8,"articleId":"4bbe06d518"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji14","name":"毛泽东全集第14卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji14.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji14":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7e02286623","type":"paragraph","text":"关于陇东问题谈判的条件","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"4bbe06d518"},{"id":"696f742cd9","type":"paragraph","text":"给谢觉战的信！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"4bbe06d518"},{"id":"e71e1b73ef","type":"paragraph","text":"（1940年1月8日）觉截同志（甲）陇东六县（环县、庆阳、合水、宁县、正宁、镇原）属达区二十三县范围，地方行政应即全部移交边区管辖，杜绝一切纠纷之源：（乙）边区及八路军保证不向六县境外越出一步：（丙）在上列两条基本原则下具体解决彼方从六县撤退军队保安队行政机关及此次纠纷中双方交换停房等事：（丁）如彼方不愿照此解决，则我只能承认双方停止冲突，暂维现状，交换仔房，其他问题，由双方中央解决。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"4bbe06d518"},{"id":"423665044b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛王肃","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"4bbe06d518"},{"id":"0bea27c9e0","type":"paragraph","text":"八日[11这是毛泽东和王橡样、萧劲光关于陇东六县问题给八路军驻兰州办","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"4bbe06d518"}],"page":{"id":"a4ef9d614a","publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"4bbe06d518","start":284,"end":284}}}},"__N_SSG":true}